', N'<p>Hi {Username},</p><p><span style="font-size: 18px;"><b>Password Reset</b></span><span style="font-size: 14px;">﻿</span></p><p>If you''ve lost your password or wish to reset it, use the link below to get started.</p><p>{Button}</p><p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Only a person with access to your email can reset your account password.</p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center; ">Problems or qustions? Call us at {CompanyPhone}</p><p style="text-align: center; ">or email&nbsp;<span style="background-color: var(--colorBackground); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);">{CompanyEmail}</span></p><p style="text-align: center; "><span style="color: rgb(77, 81, 86); font-family: arial, sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; background-color: var(--colorBackground); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);">©</span><span style="background-color: var(--colorBackground); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);">&nbsp;{CompanyName}&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: var(--colorBackground); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);">{CompanyAddress}</span></p>
